                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 163va: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ዘራስ፡ ስብሐት፡ ዘወሀቦ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ንህብ፡ ወስመ፡ ጥምቀቱ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ኪዳነ፡ ማርያም፡ ወአስማተ፡ ደቂቁ፡ ወልደ፡ ገብርኤል፡ አርአያ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወልደ፡ አረጋዊ፡ ዘመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሥምረተ፡ አብ፡ ሰበነ፡ ማርያም፡...</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol.163va: This is the book of ras Səbḥat which he donated to (the church of) St. Michael Nəhəb, and his baptismal name is Kidanä Maryam and the names of his children (are) Wäldä Gäbrəˀel, ˀArˀaya Śəllase, Wäldä ˀArägäwi, Zä-Mänfäs Qəddus, Śəmrätä ˀAb, Säbänä Maryam...</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Excerpts from hymns for the Good Friday (?) added in the upper margin: fols. 101v, 102r, 102v, 107v, 108r, 108v, 120v, 121r, 121v, 127v.&#xD;
- Corrections written with blue pen: fol. 51r.&#xD;
- Stamp with the name of the donor (ras Sǝbḥat): fols. 1r, 55r, 95r, 142r, 164r, 174r.</item>
